chilliwebs.ezjdo.com.annotations

Annotation Type BaseConfig


  • @Documented
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface BaseConfig
    Indicates how the object makes a connection to the database and the default table name to use.

    Both sqlDriverClass and connectionString are required, but table name is not, this is because the table name is generated from the object class name.
